name: Carries Kiddie Closet
tag_list: personalized-note-cards, stationery, invitations, gift-tags, labels, candy-wrappers, favors, chore-charts
overview:
Carries Kiddie Closet creates stylish and fun announcements, invitations, personalized note cards and stationery that celebrates your own unique style.

Carries Kiddie Closet features personalized note cards, invitations, boxed stationery, gift tags and labels. Our fun and affordable personalized notes, stationery, and cute invitation designs are perfect to use for your next birthday party, baby shower, bridal shower, wedding, graduation, First Communion, thank you cards, writing fun notes or any special event. We also carry baby announcements, pregnancy announcements, note cards, chore charts & gifts.
